OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and dry day with spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine for much of the region.
OL,7,FPatchy cloud likely further west
OL,8,Facross Cornwall, especially during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling warm with light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud across the far west
OL,13,Fwill drift eastwards at times
OL,14,Fthroughout the night, with a little
OL,15,Fdrizzle in places. Turning murky
OL,16,Fparticularly near the coast and over
OL,17,Fhills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
