OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,6,Fbut a band of rain will move eastwards
OL,7,Fduring the morning. Turning brighter
OL,8,Fbehind with the odd shower but feeling
OL,9,Fcooler than today.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,12,Funsettled on Friday and Saturday with
OL,13,Ffurther rain at times, mainly on
OL,14,FSaturday. Turning more showery again
OL,15,Fon Sunday. Temperatures nearer to
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
